data.description: Welcome to this cozy bungalow located in the heart of Lodi in a desirable neighborhood near many amenities. Inside you will love the floor plan with over 1000 sq feet of living space. Functional kitchen, sunny breakfast nook with plenty of space for entertaining. This is an older home but with a little love and TLC the possibilities are endless. So much potential lies within the walls of this home. The right person can, make it shine again. Plenty of room for parking plus a 2 car garage, the back yard is idea for BBQ'S and family gatherings. Take the opportunity to own a piece of Lodi history and make this classic charmer your own space to call home .
